@node "arexxinterface" " MUIEcon - ARexx: INTERFACE COMMANDS "
   @{b}LOCKGUI@{ub}
      DESCRIPTION
         This command inhibits the graphical interface of the application.
         It puts all windows to "sleep" until reversed by an @{b}UNLOCKGUI@{ub}
         command.

      RETURNS
         none


   @{b}UNLOCKGUI@{ub}
      DESCRIPTION
         This command enables the graphical interface of the application.
         It awakens all windows put to "sleep" by a @{b}LOCKGUI@{ub} command.

      RETURNS
         none
@endnode

