   @{b}Cannot open asl.library 37+@{ub}
   @{b}Cannot open utility.library 37+@{ub}
      ·  An Amiga system library could not be found.  Libraries should
         be in your LIBS: path.
      ·  MUIEcon requires version 37 or higher of each library.  This
         corresponds to AmigaDOS 2.04 or higher.  MUIEcon will not
         run without these libraries.  See also @{" Requirements " link "requirements"}.

      Use the AmigaDOS @{b}VERSION@{ub} command to determine the
      version of the libraries you are using.

   @{b}Cannot open muimaster.library@{ub}
      MUIEcon requires MUI Release 2.0 or higher.

      Use the AmigaDOS @{b}VERSION@{ub} command to determine the
      version of the libraries you are using.
@endnode

@node "errors" "MUIEcon - Error Messages"
   @{b}Cannot access printer.@{ub}
      ·  Is the printer turned on?
      ·  Is it connected to the Amiga? (If not, save your data to disk
            and turn off the computer BEFORE connecting the printer!)
      ·  Perhaps your printer settings are incorrect.  Try the 'Printer
            Setup' option in the Project menu.  For further information
            on Printer Preferences, consult your Amiga System Manual.

   @{b}Cannot open data file because ...@{ub}
      Gives a specific reason why the data file could not be opened.
      Consult your AmigaDOS manual for further details.

   @{b}Disk read error!@{ub}
      Data could not be read from the disk.
      ·  The file may be corrupt.  Try a file restoration utility.

   @{b}Disk write error! ... The data file may be corrupt.@{ub}
      Occurs if data cannot be written to the disk for some reason.
      ·  Is the disk write-protected?
      ·  Is there enough room for the file?

   @{b}File open error!@{ub}
      There was an error opening the data file.
      ·  Did you specify the name and full path correctly?

   @{b}This field cannot be zero.@{ub}
      Processing cannot continue until you enter an amount above zero.

   @{b}This field is required.@{ub}
      Processing cannot continue until you enter data in this field.

   @{b}Unable to launch Printer Preferences tool!@{ub}
      Couldn't run the Printer Preferences tool.  MUIEcon expects the
      tool to be located in SYS:Prefs and named "Printer".  That is,
      "SYS:Prefs/Printer".  If not, you'll need to access your printer's
      settings from the Amiga Workbench.

   @{b}Unable to launch the specified macro!@{ub}
      The macro (or ARexx script) you specified could not be run for
      some reason.
@endnode
